<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5029193>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Mononchoides macrospiculum Troccoli, Oreste, Tarasco, Fanelli and De Luca, 2015 (scanning electron microscopy). (a, b) Lip region (arrow pointing to the phasmid); (c, d) cuticle (having numerous bacteria along the longitudinal grooves); (f–h) male posterior end. GP = genital papilla; ph = phasmid." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5029193/files/figure.png" .

